Global Human Varicella-Zoster Immunoglobulin Market Insights
Human Varicella-Zoster Immunoglobulin Market size was valued at USD 0.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 0.9 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Human Varicella-Zoster Immunoglobulin Market Overview
The global Human Varicella-Zoster Immunoglobulin (VZIG) market is projected to grow significantly, with an estimated market value of approximately USD 1.3 billion by 2025. This growth is driven by an increasing awareness of the prevention of varicella-zoster virus (VZV) related diseases, coupled with a rise in demand for post-exposure prophylaxis in high-risk individuals. The market is also seeing advancements in the formulation of VZIG products that promise greater efficacy and improved patient safety. Key players in the market include large pharmaceutical companies, and the expansion of healthcare infrastructure in emerging markets is expected to further fuel demand.

